Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功早起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,起得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為天氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮也要曬被子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魚乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早起的鳥兒有蟲吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竹莢魚夾子夾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就這麼精神飽滿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}「5月18日  \N歌唱的油酥鬆餅」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}（一大早便是我fashion check特搜部的西井～）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不上課的話就連床單一起洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼在星期日就沒有幹勁了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經這個時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就在戶外寫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寫生場所只要是在學校內就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過可不能出學校喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點…太得意忘形了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,起床就一口氣喝了不少牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮你對牛奶過敏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平時都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是偶爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想用顏料的也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過得按時完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼主題都行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,草坪上的裸體之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危險的東西不行喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會和你一樣做那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  甚麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以去一趟洗手間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你臉色很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼難受的話最好先去保健室休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡到家還更近些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比剛才好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就在這周圍找找有甚麼可畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  戶外寫生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到甚麼好的主題了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了學生我可是不吝惜給予幫助的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如「鮮花與校長」甚麼的怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說那還太難了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學校內還有很多不熟悉的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真不知道在這種地方有竹林呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竹林…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…仙人球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:15.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（發音同為チクリン）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這事對任何人都不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幽會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…會是甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地藏菩薩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得這麼髒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來  爸爸現在還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一陣子沒聯繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上次打電話的時候還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,工作很忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不像爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:05:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有這麼髒的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了這麼個隱蔽場所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經沒事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地藏菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太髒了所以把他弄乾淨些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃門前地藏菩薩的謝禮會堆得山一般高的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要做些甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  發現好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地藏菩薩  也賞賜我些甚麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我排在由乃之後就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是斗笠地藏嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  真期待他的謝禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的人  危險～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:06:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐  弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是國際玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是沙英打這麼遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,體育課打網球真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你們是實踐課？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校內的戶外寫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那玩意學校裏有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？大夥兒都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在看山吹地藏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？沙英知道的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才是第一次看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是知道名字而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在山吹高中內所以才叫山吹地藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來還有名字的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把他搬回公寓去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就變成「暖陽地藏」了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮會招來懲罰的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我覺得不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得快些回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英打得那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發球也很厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,強到勝過男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼說沙英學姐是男生也不為過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然為過！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快點走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,new-half？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,(new-half:瑞穗)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼是new-quarter？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「寫給由乃」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「在鄉下收穫了很多所以送給你一些」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「和公寓的各位一起吃吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「你的爸爸媽媽」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  地藏菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陽臺上的曬著的魚乾不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是野貓甚麼的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然暗算我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那對脖子來說負擔太重了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  我分你一些蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  青蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶慰問品來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…這是我自己家裡送來的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始就是短袖襯衣的季節了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是無袖衫的季節了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐  到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上  剛才在公園…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有剩餘的話請務必給宮子我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的一百日圓特賣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  總之就是發生了不少…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  剛才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去卡拉OK嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得對尋學姐也會有些好處…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說最近會標明唱一支曲子能消耗多少卡路里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一支曲子多少千卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概十千卡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼唱三十支曲子就不要緊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正負相抵你就滿意了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}亮晶晶卡拉OK\N收費標準\N每人每30分鐘\N平時  10：00—18：00\N150日圓\N週末及節假日10：00—18：00\N200日圓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次來卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們班級聚會甚麼的經常會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（一杯免費飲料）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在考試之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要冰紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要薑汁飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃來過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在預約飲料呢  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（special service）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是415號房間的由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：她用了自謙語）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是服務台嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  鄭重其事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象不大常來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…烏龍茶和冰紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就讓我先唱了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:34.58,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（全新菜單  大阪特產  章魚燒  360日圓）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我們  身在此處的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧  開始旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事情都忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋很喜歡卡拉OK呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象一直很關注人氣歌曲排行榜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐也常一起來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不時會來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（剛才消耗的熱量  8千卡）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是8千卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是更火爆些的曲子會好些呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思再讓我唱一支吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是為了消滅可恨的脂肪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向著目標！300千卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐很認真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為甚麼要那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園發生了甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象是被別人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？被說甚麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋坐在長椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有個小女孩走到她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉著她的手說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「姐姐鬆鬆軟軟的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆鬆軟軟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象這對她打擊不小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡鬆軟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說好了不說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過尋學姐並沒有很胖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘記看卡路里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:56.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（請稍等片刻）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,10千卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  這次輪到沙英了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我的戀愛就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這哀傷之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐  呼呼～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實唱得很差很難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英真容易害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再放開些大聲些唱怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英的聲音很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓我們好好聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（第二支）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起那時的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如今不禁傷心落淚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,一個音唱到最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一曲沒有人點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒有決定好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有英文版的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮  那是外國歌曲喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來不是翻譯成英文的相同內容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 是嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄錯了弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,邦樂的話在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：邦樂，指日本音樂）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後吉野屋老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了衝擊性的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衝擊性的事實？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象多了很多裝飾品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做的時候是個更不起眼的雕刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是差不多這個樣子的像喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漫長的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,經過風吹雨淋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地改變了形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是一種雕刻的美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  說是漫長的歲月的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和現在的山吹地藏不是完全不一樣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象是她還是學生的時候做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虧我還拜了他  損失大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然磨損成那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師到底多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放學以後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不大明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但一定是衝擊性的事實之二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到甚麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在拜山吹地藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是偷偷地才祈求甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在404房間看見了吉野屋老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？山吹地藏是吉野屋老師做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不吃驚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說這也太遲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老師好象經常來這裡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前沙英由於截稿日來不了時看見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白天你不是說你對山吹地藏不是很熟悉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來好象說你只知道名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你連它是吉野屋老師做的都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英知道其實山吹地藏是吉野屋老師的作品…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,提問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衝擊性的事實之三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然知道為甚麼那時要敬拜它呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白天說不熟悉的是騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實那個山吹地藏在一部分的學生中有個傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是吉野屋老師做的地藏菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果對它祈願的話胸部就會變大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就覺得奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起胸部還是米飯和魚更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是想逼問你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  露餡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必要放在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放下一支曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唱些甚麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細看一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐屁股沒挨著椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細看一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有些在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上我在暗暗地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過已經是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這歌我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋也經常唱的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望窗外那無盡的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我享受這現在的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,這歌沒聽過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.08,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,但是歌詞確實一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.05,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非由乃同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有意思的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望窗外那無盡的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我享受這現在的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,將由乃五音不全唱出來的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,原封不動地再現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別人唱就能發現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我獨自一人黯然流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:16.48,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,西方天空的彎彎月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直連職業歌手都自歎不如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮子唱得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒有在別人面前用麥克唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小時侯我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在各個店裡唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才唱得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是受點心誘惑才唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我來唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,品嘗了杏兒糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進入夢鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要蘋果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:58.28,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,只想吃草莓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐作為一個女人很不錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪裡鬆鬆軟軟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要麼是胸部？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  絕對不是那個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？那是甚麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.36,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（剛才的熱量消耗  20千卡）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:10.91,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,20千卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐  繼續加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青蟲你怎麼處理了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  剛才不是拿了些蔬菜去尋學姐那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是由乃家裡送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面還有青蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想從窗子扔出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那是蟲子喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它會吃青菜的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易從老遠來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不是太可憐了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不大明白你們說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由於這個原因我想養大它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,養青蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能變成漂亮的蝴蝶就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？這麼做還真是由乃的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼？要養甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,青蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問是不是延時是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再三個小時…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,延時就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  還剩5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始最後衝刺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得好象瘦了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子消耗了不少卡路里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那孩子就是那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆鬆軟軟的粉紅色的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？鬆鬆軟軟的粉紅色？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆鬆軟軟是說頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐真小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…我還能長高的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必那麼在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？尋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（新品乳酪）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經送來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,減肥果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我嘗一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮你會吃掉一周的量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陽臺上嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被子放外面忘記收了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的魚乾…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已經不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然又濕漉漉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本應該變的鬆鬆軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬆鬆軟軟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋學姐真是夠嗆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都唱那麼賣力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃一個不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重了一公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在卡拉OK吃果凍的話會有效果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂變長了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快牛奶的效果就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是不可能的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宮真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天要兩個人一起lulululu的喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:09.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（意義不明…是忘詞了吧…）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,5月18日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天校長又發脾氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為吉野屋老師就那麼著了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來不是因為我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.47,0:23:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後我好努力想把布魯圖斯弄白的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布魯圖斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  給我麵粉的不正是沙英學姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次是「2月13日  心靈和身體」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在暖陽莊等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要來看哦
